score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T01:16:56.000Z","msg":"打乜game都係打緊大陸game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T02:03:58.000Z","msg":"鬼叫歐美冇人肯洗錢投資咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T02:11:34.000Z","msg":"同新聞媒體一樣<br />\n支那根本唔係要賺錢<br />\n而係要收集情報 <br />\n遊戲公司冇能力同燒錢的中共競爭<br />\n中共可以蝕住同你鬥燒錢<br />\n又或者出高價買game當買情報"},{"pid":"4b45fc2afc173fbbf8545353308a7ab10fe9fcdb","tid":2264712,"uid":74935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T02:15:19.000Z","msg":"可惜太多豬淨係識打機<br />\n同班豬講中資會比佢地屌返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}